    <entry>
      <title>二分法</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/09/algorithom-0/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/09/algorithom-0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>虽然二分法是算法中非常基础的算法，但是其中仍然包含了很多需要理解和熟练掌握的技巧，在这里做一个简单的归纳。结合诸多经验和网络资料，将其归纳为<strong>模版一：两种取值范围</strong>对应的两种写法和<strong>模版二：两种中值划分方式</strong>对应的两种写法。</p><h2 id="二分法技巧"><a href="#二分法技巧" class="headerlink" title="二分法技巧"></a>二分法技巧</h2><h4 id="两种写法对应两个范围"><a href="#两种写法对应两个范围" class="headerlink" title="两种写法对应两个范围"></a>两种写法对应两个范围</h4><h5 id="第一种写法（左闭右闭区间）"><a href="#第一种写法（左闭右闭区间）" class="headerlink" title="第一种写法（左闭右闭区间）"></a>第一种写法（左闭右闭区间）</h5><p>我们将 target 定义在一个左右均闭合的区间中，<strong>即在 [left, right]区间中</strong>。</p><p>相应地，这个区间决定了<strong>while的退出条件和右指针的取值方式</strong>:</p><ul><li>while (left &lt;&#x3D; right) ，因为left &#x3D;&#x3D; right是有意义的，所以需要在跳出前对该位置的值进行判断</li><li>if (nums[middle] &gt; target)， right &#x3D; middle - 1，因为当前 right &#x3D; middle 的位置检查过了，且这个nums[middle]一定不是target，不要重复检查。</li></ul><p>退出时有两种情况：</p><ul><li>满足 nums[middle] &#x3D;&#x3D; target 从中间跳出</li><li>没有满足 nums[middle] &#x3D;&#x3D; target 的值，left &gt; right 跳出，此时 left &#x3D;&#x3D; right + 1，<strong>如需返回边界值需要根据题意谨慎返回</strong>。</li></ul><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Solution</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">search</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> nums<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>target <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">||</span> target <span class="token operator">></span> nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">.</span>length <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">int</span> left <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> right <span class="token operator">=</span> nums<span class="token punctuation">.</span>length <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">while</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>left <span class="token operator">&lt;=</span> right<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">int</span> mid <span class="token operator">=</span> left <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>right <span class="token operator">-</span> left<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">>></span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">==</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token keyword">return</span> mid<span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                left <span class="token operator">=</span> mid <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">></span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                right <span class="token operator">=</span> mid <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><h5 id="第二种写法-左闭右开区间"><a href="#第二种写法-左闭右开区间" class="headerlink" title="第二种写法 (左闭右开区间)"></a>第二种写法 (左闭右开区间)</h5><p>我们将 target 定义在一个左右均闭合的区间中，<strong>即在 [left, right)区间中</strong>。</p><p>相应地，这个区间决定了<strong>while的退出条件和右指针的取值方式</strong>:</p><ul><li>while (left &lt; right) ，因为left &#x3D;&#x3D; right是没有意义的，right 所指的指针不会被取到，所以不用在 left &#x3D;&#x3D; right 上再进行判断（已经在循环中被判断过了）。</li><li>if (nums[middle] &gt; target)， right &#x3D; middle，因为当前 right &#x3D; middle 的位置检查过了，而在下一次循环中 right 指针所指的值不会被检查，所以需要使得 right &#x3D; middle 来规避nums[middle - 1]被遗漏的情况。</li></ul><p>退出时有两种情况：</p><ul><li>满足 nums[middle] &#x3D;&#x3D; target 从中间跳出。</li><li>没有满足 nums[middle] &#x3D;&#x3D; target 的值，left &gt;&#x3D; right 跳出，大多数情况下 left &#x3D;&#x3D; right，<strong>如果需要返回边界，为了不越界往往返回right</strong>。</li></ul><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Solution</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">search</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> nums<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">int</span> left <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> right <span class="token operator">=</span> nums<span class="token punctuation">.</span>length<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">while</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>left <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> right<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">int</span> mid <span class="token operator">=</span> left <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>right <span class="token operator">-</span> left<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">>></span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">==</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                <span class="token keyword">return</span> mid<span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                left <span class="token operator">=</span> mid <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>nums<span class="token punctuation">[</span>mid<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">></span> target<span class="token punctuation">)</span>                right <span class="token operator">=</span> mid<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token operator">&amp;</span>#<span class="token number">125</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><h4 id="两种写法对应两个中值划分方式"><a href="#两种写法对应两个中值划分方式" class="headerlink" title="两种写法对应两个中值划分方式"></a>两种写法对应两个中值划分方式</h4><p>统一将判断条件定位 <code>while(left &lt; right)</code>，根据划分区间的不同选择不同的模板</p><h5 id="mid-x3D-l-r-x2F-2"><a href="#mid-x3D-l-r-x2F-2" class="headerlink" title="mid &#x3D; (l + r)&#x2F;2"></a>mid &#x3D; (l + r)&#x2F;2</h5><p>此时，区间<code>[left, right]</code>被划分为分成 <code>[left, mid]</code> 和 <code>[mid + 1, right]</code>，因此，在更新时<code>right = mid</code></p><h5 id="mid-x3D-l-r-1-x2F-2"><a href="#mid-x3D-l-r-1-x2F-2" class="headerlink" title="mid &#x3D; ( l + r + 1 ) &#x2F;2"></a>mid &#x3D; ( l + r + 1 ) &#x2F;2</h5><p>此时，区间<code>[left, right]</code>被划分为分成 <code>[left, mid - 1]</code> 和 <code>[mid, right]</code>，因此，在更新时<code>right = mid + 1</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
